column8: There is a lock here... And some splitted pieces. Should I try to put them back?
I can't keep solving this stupid lock forever.

column7: Let me see if there is other way out...
Like where that something run to...

column8: I don't have time to solve this!
Is this the person that run past? I'm not sure...
Any idea who is this body?

column7: Ah... Not really... Might be a member in those Bad guys.

column8: Am I?... I remember, he was one of the guy that chased and locked me before.
I don't know... The bad people might kill each other for other reasons.
Hi! Can you see me! Can you hear me?
What? Oh my god! It's you! You REALLY exist!
Wha..Do you know me? Do you know why I'm here?
Sure! We... are looking for you! For a long time! You are the saver to the world!
The prophesy says The Saver would come to our world and clean the world, we should find him and invite him before the Bad people find him first.
That part is a little unclear in the prophecy but we believe The Saver would wipe out all Bad people and only left good ones.
Yes the Bad people are trying to kill you but don't worry, we good people will protect you and invite you to our world.
What do you mean by invite me?
Oh it's simple, just open the door from our side.
So there is a door on your side and you can just open it? Then what are we waiting for? Open it!
Well there is a tiny problem...
Skip the chat and open the door for me first!
I'd love to.. But I'm locked now...
Those bad people, take care, they are hunting you and if they found you first, They might hurt you.
Is there a way I can unlock you?
We can find the keys for me!
Yes, The Saver should have an ability to link with a human, share vision and thoughts.
Hey I can see from your sight now! Neat!
And I can hear from you directly like you are sit next to me. A little weird.
Any idea what should we do now?
Search around and see if we can find the key for me.
Now open the door for me!
I'm sorry. I'm not a good person, I burst into this place trying to kill you.
The God would not forgive me. I know. But I can't die...Sorry.
I'm sorry. I'm not a good person, I burst into this place trying to kill you.
But I think you are a good person... A good saver. Please, can you stay there and don't come out?
Awesome! I can't believe things can be so easy. What can I do now to get the key?
I know you can fetch small items from here... But the problem is, he is holding the key, so if we try fetch it, we might wake him up and put you into dangerous...
If only there is a way to take him away.
When I get out we can use it to run away.
You are the Saver! We don't need to run away, just kill them all. Haha.
Why do we need to run away?
I mean... Here are so many bad people...
You are right, I'm not getting used to my position.
They might be bad but are they deserve to die...?
They killed people, that must be count as bad people right?
Hey I see, the horse is linked to the man with key by the rope!
Oh yeah! If we provoke the horse and it runs away, we might be able to make the kay man go away!
I wonder if there is anything we can do with the horse.
Let's try using it to open the lock.
I doubt... But consider this is a game jam game and the developer is dying now I think it is the time to end the journey.
